title: War of the Roses: The Roller Dog Receipt
description: Sam has been a little suspicious that his girlfriend Zoey has a thing for a guy in a band that she always goes and sees.  He recently found a receipt for roller dogs in their garage and knows she wouldn't eat them so now he wondering where that came from or WHO was eating those roller dogs.
